summary:
Work Experience Summary:

I have gained diverse professional experience across various roles in the field of education and medicine. As a medical intern at Jinzhou University, I had the opportunity to work in a clinical setting, applying my theoretical knowledge to real-world patient care. This experience allowed me to develop a deeper understanding of medical practices and enhance my clinical skills.

Additionally, I served as a physiology and anatomy AP program teacher, where I guided students through the intricacies of the human body. This role allowed me to share my passion for the subject while helping students grasp complex concepts effectively.

Furthermore, I served as an IBDP Chemistry grade 12 teacher, imparting knowledge and fostering critical thinking skills among high school students. This experience enabled me to engage students in the fascinating world of chemistry, preparing them for their final exams and future academic pursuits.

Moreover, I held the position of Secondary School coordinator, where I played a pivotal role in overseeing the coordination and administration of various academic programs. This role required strong organizational and leadership skills, as I managed curriculum development, faculty support, and student welfare.

Certification-wise, I hold an MBBS degree, which signifies my completion of medical studies and allows me to practice medicine. I am also certified in teaching IBDP chemistry, demonstrating my expertise in delivering an internationally recognized curriculum. Additionally, I have a certification as a secondary school coordinator, showcasing my proficiency in managing educational programs and fostering a positive learning environment.

Currently, I am eagerly awaiting the start of my Global Health Masters degree, where I aim to further expand my knowledge and skills in the field of public health. This program will provide me with a comprehensive understanding of global health challenges and equip me with the tools to make a meaningful impact in improving healthcare worldwide.
